Often hailed as the best milliner in the
world, Stephen’s fashion fans and followers include Italian Vogue’s 
Anna Piaggi and Hamish Bowles of Vogue USA.

He has also collaborated with some of the fashion world’s most 
influential designers such as Marc Jacobs, Giles Deacon, Christian Dior 
and Comme des Garcons.

'We are thrilled to add Stephen to our designer offer, given his amazing industry track record and flair for his craft,' said Debenhams' director of accessories, Susie Calvert.

'He really is one of the very first, original couture milliners and it’s an honour to work with him on his Debenhams collection.'

