The department store, which will sell the collection in 28 high street outlets, online and via their mobile app, has form when it comes to hiring big name designers to produce low cost capsule collections.

Already on the Debenhams books are Henry Holland, Jenny Packham, Julien Macdonald and John Rocha.

The store also recently signed up Jenny Packham, one of the Duchess of Cambridge's favourite pre-pregnancy couturiers. 

